rstood without a historical account of the global political mobilization of liberal Protestants.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aGlobalizationxReligious aspectsxProtestant churches. 0aHuman rightsxReligious aspectsxProtestant churchesxHistoryy20th century. 0aLiberalism (Religion)xProtestant churchesxHistoryy20th century. 0aLiberalismzUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolarization (Social sciences)zUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aProtestant churcheszUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aProtestantismzUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / United States / 20th Century.2bisacsh  aAmerican History.  aAmerican Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishz978311099296008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022z9783110992939oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Pennsylvania Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076767440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780812298291423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780812298291/original  a978-3-11-076767-4  University of Pennsylvania Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099296-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022